Thornmother's fall exposed the Ashfang command lattice that had been using her confusion mists as battlefield cover. Kowloon covenant marshals now require a coordinated purge of both remaining Ashfang war leaders before they can regroup and rearm the border camps. Cut down the war-chief and the warmaster to end organized ashfang pressure on the northern charter road.
Both Ashfang commanders are dead, and intercepted battle-calls indicate no surviving officer has authority to unify the splintered warbands. Kowloon customs patrols report that ambush banners have been stripped from the old ridge chokepoints. The covenant road is open for the final spiritual cleansing phase.
